name: GoodDay
0:
”Alexa open good day”

skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: good day
des: Do you want to start your day in a positive way first thing in the morning, or hear the day’s good news before going to bed? Positive Day brings you positive news! It's time to hear a piece of good news from a range of different categories: UK, World, Science, Environment. You can choose to hear all of them, which are the latest news from Positive. News. The latest stories will live update based on their website. You can say help to recall the four categories name.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
